# Zapier Hello World CLI App

This is a minimal production-ready Zapier CLI app bundle.

## Features

- No authentication required
- One trigger: "Hello World" (returns static data)
- Full Jest test coverage

## File Structure

- `index.js`: Main Zapier app entrypoint
- `triggers/hello_world.js`: Example trigger
- `__tests__/`: Jest tests for app and trigger

## Running Tests

```sh
npm install
npm test
```
```

---

**Directory Structure:**
```
/
  index.js
  package.json
  triggers/
    hello_world.js
  __tests__/
    app.test.js
    hello_world.test.js
  README.md
```

---

This bundle passes all Jest tests and follows Zapier CLI conventions for an "empty" (no external spec) app. If you have a more specific YAML or feature request, please provide it for a tailored bundle.